             were indicted for <rs id="t17880625-83-off375" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880625-83-off375" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880625-83-off375" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing on the <rs id="t17880625-83-cd376" type="crimeDate">10th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880625-83-off375 t17880625-83-cd376"></join>, a silver watch, value 4 l. a steal seal, value 3 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17880625-83-victim741" type="victimName">
                           Christopher 
                           Finney
                        <interp inst="t17880625-83-victim741" type="surname" value="Finney"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17880625-83-victim741" type="given" value="Christopher"></interp>
